<document>
    <properties>
        <title>Groups Configuration</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <section name="Groups Configuration">
            <p>
                The groups are stored in the repository as childeren of the node
                <code>/hippo:configuration/hippo:groups</code>. The members of the group are
                stored in the nulti valued property <code>hippo:members</code>
                A groups node has the following configuration:
            </p>
<source>
&lt;sv:node sv:name="mygroup"&gt;
    &lt;sv:property sv:name="jcr:primaryType" sv:type="Name"&gt;
        &lt;sv:value&gt;hippo:group&lt;/sv:value&gt;
    &lt;/sv:property&gt;
    &lt;sv:property sv:name="hippo:members" sv:type="String"&gt;
        &lt;sv:value&gt;demo&lt;/sv:value&gt;
        &lt;sv:value&gt;user1&lt;/sv:value&gt;
    &lt;/sv:property&gt;
&lt;/sv:node&gt;
</source>
            <p>
                The name of the node is used as the group name.
            </p>
            <p>
                The groups configuration is used by the <a href="../repository/authentication.html">RepositoryLoginModule</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
    </body>
</document>
